{"word":"G987 - βλασφημέω - blasphēméō - blas-fay-meh'-o - Blaspheme","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">βλασφημέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">blasphēméō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">blas-fay-meh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Blaspheme</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தூஷி, இகழு, தேவதூஷணம் சொல்லு"},{"paragraph":"to speak reproachfully, rail at, revile, calumniate"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G989 - βλάσφημος - blásphēmos - blas'-fay-mos/989\">G989</a>; to <i>vilify</i>; specifically to <i>speak impiously:</i> - (speak) blaspheme (-er, -mously, -my), defame, rail on, revile, speak evil.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G987/987\">G987</a>, <a href=\"#/G988/988\">G988</a>, <a href=\"#/G989/989\">G989</a>"}]}